{"tid":1985710,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】深圳下周一分階段復課 市衞健委首披露27師生感染","createTime":"2020-04-23T10:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T10:58:40.000Z","uid":53062,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"055047ccdcc390070755e7a59107176c75502bb8","tid":1985710,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:35:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200423/NJNQ57DJ4DOMQHXDGSTGNXKVYU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200423%2FNJNQ57DJ4DOMQHXDGSTGNXKVYU%2F&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6pgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=301d12f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200423%2FNJNQ57DJ4DOMQHXDGSTGNXKVYU%2F&h=d37532a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200423/NJNQ57DJ4DOMQHXDGSTGNXKVYU/</a><br />\n<br />\n內地武漢肺炎疫情看似平穩，深圳市昨日宣佈中小學下周一（27日）開始分階段復課，但卻首次披露有27名師生感染武肺病毒。<br />\n<br />\n截至22日，深圳累計確診個案為461宗，另有33宗無症狀感染者當在醫學觀察。深圳市衞健委副主任吳兵昨表示，該市共有6名教師感染，當中5人確診（4人已出院，1人留醫），1宗為無症狀感染者，已解除隔離；另有21名學生（小學生10宗、中學生7宗、大學生4宗）感染，其中確診個案有16宗（小學生7宗、中學生5宗，大學生4宗），均已出院；無症狀感染者5宗（小學生3宗、中學生2宗），4人已解除隔離，1人仍在醫院觀察。"},{"pid":"1d26e3aeb0fac9c971453b0d116f00f9b0e1096f","tid":1985710,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"冇眼睇"},{"pid":"91de751ca070473ff0d0d29efe0228520a27b65f","tid":1985710,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:41:50.000Z","msg":"好小事<br />\n普通感冒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7e0109e548181092a290431710c2d163b6d970","tid":1985710,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:43:29.000Z","msg":"繼續全面落實雜種的全面復課復工精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae83d0e87b643d9e2ef165194e77c5942aaea72","tid":19857